product_desc:
Hello,

My name is Jay Crouch, and I have worked as an engineer in startups for 13 years. I've raised over $10M while cofounding 4 companies, and today I am fortunate enough to consult for a multi-billion dollar startup as a Senior Software Architect.

John Shiple, another experienced CTO, and I are inviting top notch engineers to work with us on a few well paid projects which we are leading:

All clients are top-tier startups in top-tier markets (SF, LA, NY, etc)
All roles include big upside opportunities
We employ no sales people.
We have the experience and relationships to groom you into a world class Architect or Technical Officer.
We already have big name clients, and we only win when you do.

Reply to this message to learn more about working with us.
Freelance and full-time developers welcome. We work with engineers that are assertive about learning new skills.

Don't miss out on the next Unicorn opportunity, let us find it for you. 

Good luck, and happy coding.
high_concept: Just how good of an Engineer are you?
